{"tid":1565413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講好左既中秋升級 原來只係默哀唱歌","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T07:08:23.000Z","uid":287032,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a589a3b541ca822db88f52bddda25fe53969c816","tid":1565413,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:41:57.000Z","msg":"雖然話講好左兄弟爬山<br />\n但係而家好明顯有幕後勢力利用和理非騎劫勇武活動<br />\n成個9月唔係和你塞機場商場就係和你燈<br />\n班機場admin大台仲話衝鋪頭就係鬼<br />\n今晚仲打算唱歌唱到十一點半<br />\n逼大家夠鐘返屋企<br />\n<br />\n我係政府就真係輕鬆又開心<br />\n<br />\n我地一路行到今日<br />\n除左因爲和理非既支持<br />\n勇武既不斷升級都係好重要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請記住和勇缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"a05bb4960e2ee0530f32dda64403b8f7395d3250","tid":1565413,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=252cec7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"66caabfc0b3827daa9252403892b88a69c27fa3c","tid":1565413,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"49f7a73d7a13b515ee9ed75b9f0b7780032959b2","tid":1565413,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3060f70bcb7d5e41fa599ce6eb3cecb203c095e9","tid":1565413,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386a43751941dbf8ab4c437e9ad58d08daaa01f1","tid":1565413,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a7514a5c83ea1858e7155fac5d03558f286a21","tid":1565413,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唱歌唔會令政權覺得痛</span></span>"},{"pid":"fab69291c33e0d58f0ea8d962148c070856eb479","tid":1565413,"uid":287032,"lik